# Demand Forecasting & Inventory Optimization Dashboard

This project builds a **machine learning based demand forecasting and inventory optimization system** using the **Sample Superstore Dataset**.

The system predicts **future product demand**, calculates **optimal order quantity**, determines **reorder point**, and estimates the **risk of stockout** using machine learning models.

A **Streamlit dashboard** is used to interact with the models and visualize the results.

---

# Project Objective

The goal of this project is to combine **machine learning** and **inventory management techniques** to help businesses:

* Forecast product demand
* Avoid stockouts
* Reduce holding and ordering costs
* Improve inventory planning

